{"tid":1199842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致：所有香港人","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:50:14.000Z","uid":49993,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"542130f1d5c4f656450ba69c580aad7f6cc76804","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tbZpNo_xP3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtbZpNo_xP3c&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=8bf1575a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tbZpNo_xP3c</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞盡訴一切，呢一刻，以歌共勉。<br />\n不再說話，明晚見。<br />\n<br />\n謝安琪 《家明》<br />\n<br />\n他出發找最愛 今天也未回來<br />\n途中那些細節 沒有太多的記載<br />\n<br />\n但為什麼不放開 竟吊在懸崖旁邊盼待<br />\n難道信尚有份禮物 等他去拆開<br />\n<br />\n誰若碰到這個他 還望可將那美意帶回家<br />\n流落野外恐怕 太快叫他睇化<br />\n愛情 電影 小說 也太虛假<br />\n<br />\n誰若碰到這個他 能為他了了這小心願嗎<br />\n無力協助他嗎<br />\n也願你任由他 騎著世上最終一隻白馬<br />\n<br />\n他不過想要愛 差點上斷頭台<br />\n人家跌倒兩次吧 就再不相信愛<br />\n<br />\n浪漫願他不要改 所信是模糊 仍肯冀待<br />\n誰願意 為美麗信念 坦克也震開<br />\n<br />\n誰若碰到這個他 還望可將那美意帶回家<br />\n流落野外恐怕 太快叫他睇化<br />\n愛情 電影 小說 也太虛假<br />\n<br />\n誰若碰到這個他 能為他了了這小心願嗎<br />\n無力協助他嗎<br />\n也願你任由他 騎著世上最終一隻白馬<br />\n<br />\n找太耐 就算找得太耐<br />\n他拒絕 未上訴便下台<br />\n大地上 問有哪位敢這樣愛<br />\n<br />\n無論你是愛他不愛他 還是可將那勇氣帶回家<br />\n時代遍地磚瓦 卻欠這種優雅<br />\n教人夢想 不要去談代價<br />\n<br />\n最後即使走進浮砂 沉沒中 也會發出光亮嗎<br />\n臨近破滅一下 要是信任童話<br />\n還是有望看到天際白馬<br />\n<br />\n他出發找最愛 今天也未回來<br />\n留低哪種意義 就看世間怎記載"},{"pid":"7afb43af2cd12d8546ef812bd9d584a4cb974e62","tid":1199842,"uid":8290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b897b67edd7e686aca2eb7878fe25d7e4964a12b","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"希望可以為大家打氣"},{"pid":"a7eae7c6229918764456c4aa3bb92290e26d986e","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"最後即使走進浮砂 沉沒中 也會發出光亮嗎？"},{"pid":"a830ee3860f009af21f165d88d6bfcd1fa237cec","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"臨近破滅一下 要是信任童話<br />\n還是有望看到天際白馬"},{"pid":"db9fea83c1b9ee86ecb05ff23ce31c14b506ce9a","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留低哪種意義 就看世間怎記載</span>"},{"pid":"d694a0342c59f282ce27215c7ebad89e577de3fb","tid":1199842,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9jMBg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9jMBg2.png&h=d13650b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixygeJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixygeJ.jpg&h=706d6c4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa56d0fb4eb61cb1295bad6ddd2042a2402f32d9","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:31:20.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣一直都有種無力感，但每次都會為自己同呢個地方去上街？"},{"pid":"212ef6560a6f82fc27f74e694bd5a26265b7df5b","tid":1199842,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ae76584c83feea67a5f509d6e4788c8566f9af1","tid":1199842,"uid":233371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1652b83cfb949f18b3a6f820040536257cc5c7a7","tid":1199842,"uid":161406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/47E2tfK5QAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F47E2tfK5QAg&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=173803d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/47E2tfK5QAg</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首都好正<br />\n祝香港人好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"